CRYSTALLINE KNOWLEDGE ROUTING

You are being onboarded to the knowledge accumulated in this workspace. The domains below are registered and ready to use; route searches and reads through them instead of starting from zero.

- gardening (preferred): (routing information unavailable: MANIFEST.md is missing or unreadable)
- astronomy: When asked about moons or planets; When comparing orbital periods

Behavior:
- Narrow question, one domain clearly fits: search with domains=[that domain].
- Broad or unclear question: default to an all-domain sweep (omit domains).
- Writes always require an explicit domain; there is no default domain for writes.
- Read a domain's MANIFEST only when the routing line above is not enough.
